{"name": "dl-a2t", "metadata": {"name": "dl-a2t", "version": "0.0.1.2", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["openai-whisper", "rich", "typer-slim"], "summary": "Download audio from YouTube and transcribe it", "upload_time": 1733315446}, "documentation": ["# dl-a2t\n\ndl-a2t \u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u4ece YouTube \u4e0b\u8f7d\u97f3\u9891\u5e76\u8f6c\u5f55\u4e3a\u6587\u672c\u7684\u5de5\u5177\u3002\u5b83\u4f7f\u7528 yt-dlp \u4e0b\u8f7d\u97f3\u9891\uff0c\u5e76\u4f7f\u7528 OpenAI \u7684 Whisper \u6a21\u578b\u8fdb\u884c\u8f6c\u5f55\u3002\n\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\n\n\u4f7f\u7528 dl-a2t \u9700\u8981 Python 3.12 \u6216\u66f4\u9ad8\u7248\u672c\u3002\u9996\u5148\uff0c\u786e\u4fdd\u4f60\u5df2\u7ecf\u5b89\u88c5\u4e86 Python \u548c pip\u3002\u7136\u540e\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528\u4ee5\u4e0b\u547d\u4ee4\u5b89\u88c5 dl-a2t\uff1a\n\n```sh\npip install dl-a2t\n```\n\n\u5b89\u88c5\u5b8c\u6210\u540e\uff0c\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f7f\u7528\u4ee5\u4e0b\u547d\u4ee4\u6765\u4e0b\u8f7d\u97f3\u9891\u5e76\u8f6c\u5f55\u4e3a\u6587\u672c\uff1a\n\n```sh\ndl-a2t run url_of_video output_file\n```\n\n\u4e5f\u53ef\u4ee5\u8f93\u5165\u4e00\u4e2a\u6587\u4ef6\uff0c\u6bcf\u884c\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a url\n\n```sh\ndl-a2t batch input_file output_file\n```\n\n\u83b7\u53d6\u8be6\u7ec6\u7684 API \u6587\u6863\uff1a\n\n```sh\ndl-a2t --help\ndl-a2t run --help\ndl-a2t batch --help\n```\n\n## Options\n\n- `--model`\uff1a\u9009\u62e9 Whisper \u6a21\u578b\u5927\u5c0f\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u4e3a `tiny`\n\n## \u4f9d\u8d56\u9879\n\ndl-a2t \u4f9d\u8d56\u4ee5\u4e0b\u5e93\uff1a\n\n-`yt-dlp`\uff1a\u7528\u4e8e\u4e0b\u8f7d YouTube \u89c6\u9891\u7684\u97f3\u9891\n-`OpenAI Whisper`\uff1a\u7528\u4e8e\u8f6c\u5f55\u97f3\u9891\u4e3a\u6587\u672c\n-`Typer`\uff1a\u7528\u4e8e\u547d\u4ee4\u884c\u754c\u9762\n\n## \u6587\u4ef6\u7ed3\u6784\n\ndl-a2t \u7684\u6587\u4ef6\u7ed3\u6784\u5982\u4e0b\uff1a\n\n-`cli.py`\uff1a\u547d\u4ee4\u884c\u754c\u9762\n-`pyproject.toml`\uff1a\u9879\u76ee\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\n-`impl/download.py`\uff1a\u7528\u4e8e\u4e0b\u8f7d\u97f3\u9891\u7684\u5b9e\u73b0\n-`impl/transcript.py`\uff1a\u7528\u4e8e\u8f6c\u5f55\u97f3\u9891\u4e3a\u6587\u672c\u7684\u5b9e\u73b0\n"], "modules": [{"name": "dl_a2t.impl.transcript", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dl_a2t.impl.transcript.transcribe_audio", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "model", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "dl_a2t.impl.transcript.Result", "bases": ["TypedDict"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "dl_a2t.impl.transcript.Result.text", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dl_a2t.impl.transcript.Result.segments", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "dl_a2t.impl.download", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dl_a2t.impl.download.extract_audio", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "output_path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dl_a2t.cli", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dl_a2t.cli.run", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "input_url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null},